00:22.139 --> 00:30.295
When it's sunny, I like to go and do a walk or do a bike ride.

00:30.961 --> 00:37.093
And then, it's gonna be all cloudy and windy at 5 o'clock.

00:38.608 --> 00:44.727
When it's cloudy, I like to see what kind of shapes they are.

00:45.667 --> 00:50.587
And then at 9 o'clock, it's gonna be windy.

00:54.799 --> 01:01.426
When it's windy, I like to play with my brother.

01:02.414 --> 01:10.451
